.TH "snd_dmaengine_pcm_request_channel" 9 "snd_dmaengine_pcm_request_channel" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
snd_dmaengine_pcm_request_channel \- Request channel for the dmaengine PCM
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "struct dma_chan *" snd_dmaengine_pcm_request_channel
.BI "(dma_filter_fn filter_fn "  ","
.BI "void *filter_data "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "filter_fn" 12
Filter function used to request the DMA channel
.IP "filter_data" 12
Data passed to the DMA filter function
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Returns NULL or the requested DMA channel.

This function request a DMA channel for usage with dmaengine PCM.
